description:
What is it: A dynamic device group that is used for assigning the User-Driven Intune Autopilot profile to devices. 
 Simeon Notes: Includes all devices that are not in the Azure AD group, 'BUILTIN - Autopilot Devices - Self Deploying'. 
 Learn More: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/mem/autopilot/user-driven
